Example data

Source: R/data.R
dfi_example.Rd

Example of DFI values. This is dummy data. A vector with 121 DFI-values between 1 and 0. The index is decreasing monotonously with larger n. This can be used for testing the find_bps function.

Usage

dfi_example

Format

vector data

Examples

data(dfi_example)
